            <lg xml:id="TK258">
<l>ceyiriṟ ṟalaippirinta kāṭciyā ruṇṇā</l>
<l>ruyiriṟ ṟalaippirinta vūṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wise, who have freed themselves from mental delusion, will not eat the flesh which has been severed from an animal.</l>
